# Mobile Development Environment Setup
- Ensure Xcode is installed from the App Store for iOS development
- Configure proper UTF-8 encoding for CocoaPods
- Maintain sufficient disk space (keep at least 20% free)
- Clear NX cache if encountering SQLite errors
- Use React Native and Expo for cross-platform development
- Follow mobile-first design principles
- Implement proper error handling and loading states
- Ensure proper permissions handling for mobile features
